I'll introduce her to you later.

41
00:04:51,350 --> 00:04:52,110
No hurry.

42
00:04:58,270 --> 00:04:58,930
Xie.

43
00:04:59,600 --> 00:05:00,360
Qing.

44
00:05:01,910 --> 00:05:03,990
The female victim is not over 30 years old.

45
00:05:04,020 --> 00:05:06,220
She died less than 12 hours ago.

46
00:05:06,930 --> 00:05:09,240
Two complete shoe prints were found at the scene.

47
00:05:10,210 --> 00:05:10,970
Qing.

48
00:05:11,750 --> 00:05:12,740
You don't look well.

49
00:05:12,790 --> 00:05:13,980
Did you stay up late again?

50
00:05:14,990 --> 00:05:16,230
Do you have painkillers?

51
00:05:16,230 --> 00:05:17,310
I'm on my period.

52
00:05:17,330 --> 00:05:18,220
I'm out.

53
00:05:18,220 --> 00:05:19,220
Mine just started yesterday too.

54
00:05:19,860 --> 00:05:20,580
It's okay.

55
00:05:21,450 --> 00:05:22,020
Carry on with your work.

56
00:05:25,590 --> 00:05:30,400
[Police]

57
00:05:31,900 --> 00:05:33,980
The mountaintop collapses whenever it rains.

58
00:05:34,000 --> 00:05:35,540
Who knew something like this would turn up?

59
00:05:35,570 --> 00:05:36,720
You can say that again.

60
00:05:36,890 --> 00:05:38,110
It's too cruel.

61
00:05:38,110 --> 00:05:39,990
It looks like someone's been dismembered.

62
00:05:41,460 --> 00:05:42,540
I heard that

63
00:05:42,540 --> 00:05:44,840
there was a black plastic bag.

64
00:05:47,420 --> 00:05:48,960
The Qianzhuang Village built that

65
00:05:49,000 --> 00:05:50,430
new cement road just last year.

66
00:05:50,550 --> 00:05:53,080
I heard it from the villagers just now.

67
00:05:56,190 --> 00:05:56,920
Look.

68
00:05:58,420 --> 00:05:59,740
This is the track map.

69
00:06:00,860 --> 00:06:01,890
From that point down there

70
00:06:02,050 --> 00:06:03,540
to where we are now,

71
00:06:03,580 --> 00:06:05,740
the straight line distance is 923 meters.

72
00:06:05,980 --> 00:06:07,220
There are fields in the middle.

73
00:06:07,240 --> 00:06:09,110
We can only come up here on foot.

74
00:06:11,260 --> 00:06:12,900
It only takes a few minutes to get there

75
00:06:12,920 --> 00:06:14,140
from Route Jiangping.

76
00:06:14,870 --> 00:06:17,380
The murderer may have chosen the Jiangping Highway

77
00:06:17,740 --> 00:06:19,280
instead of the cement road below.

78
00:06:19,300 --> 00:06:20,100
That’s right.

79
00:06:20,540 --> 00:06:22,390
The Jiangping Highway is well-connected.

80
00:06:22,470 --> 00:06:24,810
It leads to the national highway and the provincial city.

81
00:06:24,990 --> 00:06:26,870
The murderer didn't need to pick the long way,

82
00:06:26,900 --> 00:06:27,730
travel in the dark,

83
00:06:27,780 --> 00:06:29,860
carry three bags of corpse parts,

84
00:06:30,100 --> 00:06:32,580
and walk over 900 meters from the cement road.

85
00:06:32,790 --> 00:06:34,110
For one, the murderer might be easily spotted.

86
00:06:34,130 --> 00:06:35,570
Two, it might increase the duration of the crime.

87
00:06:35,600 --> 00:06:38,000
Three, there would be many uncontrollable risks.

88
00:06:38,220 --> 00:06:39,240
However...

89
00:06:39,390 --> 00:06:40,750
However, they may

90
00:06:40,900 --> 00:06:43,030
avoid our detection, right?

91
00:06:43,700 --> 00:06:44,300
Yes.

92
00:06:46,060 --> 00:06:47,310
Jiangping Highway

93
00:06:47,330 --> 00:06:49,020
is right under the burial site.

94
00:06:49,380 --> 00:06:51,420
Naturally, it's our first target of investigation.

95
00:06:52,630 --> 00:06:54,070
And the cement road below

96
00:06:54,159 --> 00:06:55,930
might be ignored by us.

97
00:06:56,050 --> 00:06:57,620
If I were the murderer,

98
00:06:58,530 --> 00:07:00,190
I would choose the cement road.

99
00:07:00,490 --> 00:07:02,170
To commit a perfect crime,

100
00:07:02,660 --> 00:07:04,500
you have to pay a higher price.

101
00:07:08,700 --> 00:07:09,550
Nice to meet you, Qing.

102
00:07:09,610 --> 00:07:10,620
My name is Lin Jiajia.

103
00:07:10,660 --> 00:07:12,190
It's my first day here.

104
00:07:12,420 --> 00:07:14,300
I've never seen any perfect crime.

105
00:07:14,660 --> 00:07:16,150
Because people make mistakes.

106
00:07:16,180 --> 00:07:17,620
The murderer is no exception.

107
00:07:19,750 --> 00:07:20,360
Yes.

108
00:07:34,230 --> 00:07:35,700
The two villages nearby are not big.

109
00:07:35,740 --> 00:07:36,900
Together, they have about 200 households.

110
00:07:36,900 --> 00:07:37,540
Captain Fang.

111
00:07:39,060 --> 00:07:40,150
I think

112
00:07:40,330 --> 00:07:42,570
it's unlikely that a local committed the crime.

113
00:07:42,970 --> 00:07:46,470
[Police]

114
00:07:43,180 --> 00:07:43,900
Why not?

115
00:07:44,940 --> 00:07:46,370
I heard from the villagers that

116
00:07:46,540 --> 00:07:48,270
mudslides are common when it rains here.

117
00:07:48,320 --> 00:07:50,300
This is common sense to the locals.

118
00:07:51,300 --> 00:07:52,830
If a local had committed the crime,

119
00:07:53,000 --> 00:07:55,170
the body wouldn't have been buried here.

120
00:07:56,450 --> 00:07:57,650
I saw the body part.

121
00:07:57,260 --> 00:08:00,920
[Police]

122
00:07:58,180 --> 00:07:59,300
The girl's nails

123
00:07:59,300 --> 00:08:00,540
have nail polish on them.

124
00:08:00,730 --> 00:08:02,300
She was definitely not a farmer.

125
00:08:03,450 --> 00:08:04,420
Route Jiangping

126
00:08:04,500 --> 00:08:06,500
conveniently connects to the outskirts of the city.

127
00:08:06,980 --> 00:08:07,920
I think

128
00:08:08,380 --> 00:08:10,780
it's more likely that someone drove here to dump the body.

129
00:08:10,780 --> 00:08:12,180
Notify the video team

130
00:08:12,500 --> 00:08:14,090
to check the surveillance footage of Route Jiangping

131
00:08:14,540 --> 00:08:15,620
for suspicious vehicles and people.

132
00:08:16,150 --> 00:08:17,020
Also,

133
00:08:17,040 --> 00:08:18,140
you saw that guy, right?

134
00:08:18,310 --> 00:08:21,290
He's an intern officer transferred from the provincial capital.

135
00:08:21,320 --> 00:08:23,300
Director Hou specifically asked you to mentor him.

136
00:08:23,300 --> 00:08:24,940
You're the backbone of our team now.

137
00:08:25,180 --> 00:08:26,850
You should mentor a newcomer or two, right?

138
00:08:27,180 --> 00:08:28,700
Let him be your partner.

139
00:08:29,330 --> 00:08:30,550
I have a partner.

140
00:08:30,780 --> 00:08:32,309
My partner is Zhong Wei.

141
00:08:33,690 --> 00:08:38,520
[Police]

142
00:08:33,890 --> 00:08:34,770
Yu.

143
00:08:39,580 --> 00:08:45,340
[May 6, 8:20 a.m., an hour after the mutilated bodies were found]

144
00:08:39,580 --> 00:08:45,340
[Dongzhou City Police Bureau]

145
00:08:52,700 --> 00:08:53,540
Yu.

146
00:08:53,940 --> 00:08:54,630
Qing.

147
00:08:54,660 --> 00:08:55,190
How is it?

148
00:08:55,630 --> 00:08:56,790
From the time of the incident last night

149
00:08:56,830 --> 00:08:58,060
to the time of report this morning,

150
00:08:58,080 --> 00:08:59,350
85 cars

151
00:08:59,170 --> 00:09:01,690
[Dongzhou toll station, Jiangping Road]

152
00:08:59,380 --> 00:09:01,180
passed by the dumping spot near Route Jiangping.

153
00:09:01,790 --> 00:09:03,930
Judging from the intersections on both sides,

154
00:09:04,020 --> 00:09:06,020
every car passed at the right time.

155
00:09:07,300 --> 00:09:08,660
Did any car turn back?

156
00:09:08,780 --> 00:09:10,820
No, all cars drove in one direction.

157
00:09:13,180 --> 00:09:14,570
What about the drivers' information?

158
00:09:14,820 --> 00:09:15,780
All normal.

159
00:09:15,820 --> 00:09:16,950
None of them had criminal records.

160
00:09:17,070 --> 00:09:18,110
The cars are fine too.

161
00:09:18,140 --> 00:09:19,390
No faked or covered plates.

162
00:09:22,150 --> 00:09:23,620
Check on

163
00:09:23,820 --> 00:09:27,190
the cement road Qianzhuang Village built last year.

164
00:09:25,190 --> 00:09:27,520
[Dongzhou toll station, Jiangping Road]

165
00:09:27,630 --> 00:09:28,710
The one

166
00:09:28,780 --> 00:09:31,900
more than 900 meters away from the burial site.

167
00:09:32,540 --> 00:09:33,910
Tell me if you find anything.

168
00:09:33,930 --> 00:09:34,540
Okay.

169
00:10:13,470 --> 00:10:15,020
Truly the instinct of an excellent officer.

170
00:10:15,140 --> 00:10:16,180
You're right again.

171
00:10:16,540 --> 00:10:18,380
These two cases are really related.

172
00:10:23,430 --> 00:10:24,260
Qing.

173
00:10:36,660 --> 00:10:38,390
Who told you to put things here?

174
00:10:41,030 --> 00:10:42,300
Who allowed you to sit here?

175
00:10:43,670 --> 00:10:44,700
Captain Fang.

176
00:10:46,460 --> 00:10:48,250
This table is occupied. You can't use it.

177
00:10:48,640 --> 00:10:50,440
[Police]

178
00:10:55,510 --> 00:10:57,200
Where should I sit, Qing?

179
00:11:05,160 --> 00:11:06,940
[Captain's Office]

180
00:11:07,030 --> 00:11:08,470
[High Ambitions]

181
00:11:07,580 --> 00:11:08,430
Han Qing.

182
00:11:10,490 --> 00:11:11,690
Captain Fang, what's the meaning of this?

183
00:11:13,760 --> 00:11:14,990
What do you mean?

184
00:11:15,030 --> 00:11:17,550
Why did you let Lin Jiajia sit at Zhong Wei's desk?

185
00:11:21,370 --> 00:11:22,390
Well, Lin Jiajia

186
00:11:22,420 --> 00:11:23,910
has been assigned to our team.

187
00:11:23,950 --> 00:11:25,210
He needs a seat.

188
00:11:25,660 --> 00:11:26,550
Look at this office.

189
00:11:26,660 --> 00:11:28,140
That's Zhong Wei's desk.

190
00:11:28,390 --> 00:11:29,620
Calm down.

191
00:11:29,670 --> 00:11:31,310
I know that's Zhong Wei's desk.

192
00:11:31,430 --> 00:11:32,900
Everyone in the Major Crimes Brigade knows

193
00:11:32,900 --> 00:11:33,540
that's Zhong Wei's desk.

194
00:11:33,540 --> 00:11:34,780
Then what are you implying?

195
00:11:36,060 --> 00:11:36,780
That you don't care

196
00:11:36,820 --> 00:11:38,540
about Zhong Wei anymore, right?

197
00:11:38,620 --> 00:11:39,420
Han Qing.

198
00:11:39,670 --> 00:11:41,760
What makes you think I don't care?

199
00:11:42,140 --> 00:11:43,560
When Zhong Wei first disappeared,

200
00:11:43,700 --> 00:11:45,590
I dispatched the entire team

201
00:11:45,630 --> 00:11:47,300
to work tirelessly for days.

202
00:11:47,420 --> 00:11:48,150
But we have no choice.

203
00:11:48,180 --> 00:11:50,020
We have no clues to follow.

204
00:11:50,180 --> 00:11:52,260
You can't just let Zhong Wei's disappearance

205
00:11:52,300 --> 00:11:54,060
delay all the other cases.

206
00:11:57,580 --> 00:11:58,390
Captain Fang.

207
00:11:58,660 --> 00:11:59,540
Han Qing.

208
00:11:59,480 --> 00:12:02,030
[Captain's Office]

209
00:11:59,910 --> 00:12:01,180
I restored the desk to what it was.

210
00:12:01,180 --> 00:12:02,030
I won't sit there.

211
00:12:02,480 --> 00:12:03,040
No.

212
00:12:03,060 --> 00:12:04,550
Just sit there. This has nothing to do with you.

213
00:12:04,670 --> 00:12:05,780
I found a new place to sit.

214
00:12:04,700 --> 00:12:08,500
[Captain's Office]

215
00:12:05,900 --> 00:12:06,900
My new place is good.

216
00:12:07,420 --> 00:12:08,780
Go on. I won't disturb you.

217
00:12:13,670 --> 00:12:15,550
Do you think Zhong Wei's gone forever?

218
00:12:19,410 --> 00:12:21,300
He has been missing for 52 days.

219
00:12:24,900 --> 00:12:25,740
Han Qing.

220
00:12:27,280 --> 00:12:28,220
Sometimes,

221
00:12:29,040 --> 00:12:30,560
you need to learn to accept it.

222
00:12:42,710 --> 00:12:44,030
I will find him.

223
00:12:56,930 --> 00:12:57,690
Hao,

224
00:12:57,710 --> 00:12:59,750
who's in charge of the murder case at the bathhouse?

225
00:13:00,390 --> 00:13:01,760
Zhong Wei and Han Qing.

226
00:13:02,020 --> 00:13:04,020
Aren't they in charge of Wan Haiqiang's case?

227
00:13:04,190 --> 00:13:05,650
The murder case at the bathhouse

228
00:13:05,780 --> 00:13:06,900
was also given to them.

229
00:13:06,930 --> 00:13:09,530
[Police]

230
00:13:07,150 --> 00:13:08,180
In my opinion,

231
00:13:08,300 --> 00:13:09,500
they should be split up

232
00:13:09,580 --> 00:13:11,140
to work on different cases.

233
00:13:11,260 --> 00:13:12,730
But they can't be separated.

234
00:13:12,470 --> 00:13:16,820
[Police]

235
00:13:33,920 --> 00:13:37,910
[Brave, Sagacity]

236
00:13:40,940 --> 00:13:42,950
[Dismemberment case]

237
00:14:00,880 --> 00:14:02,880
Qing, my seat is very good.

238
00:14:02,900 --> 00:14:03,870
It's close to the door.

239
00:14:03,940 --> 00:14:04,860
The air circulation is great.

240
00:14:05,000 --> 00:14:06,710
It's like camping outside.

241
00:14:07,990 --> 00:14:08,510
Yes.

242
00:14:21,570 --> 00:14:22,850
Why are you following me?

243
00:14:24,460 --> 00:14:25,830
I'm going to investigate the case with you.

244
00:14:25,870 --> 00:14:27,610
Who asked you to investigate the case with me?

245
00:14:28,150 --> 00:14:30,460
Didn’t Captain Fang ask you to lead me?

246
00:14:32,010 --> 00:14:33,360
Qing, please take me with you.

247
00:14:33,490 --> 00:14:35,530
I just want to learn from you.

248
00:14:48,060 --> 00:14:49,440
Where are we going?

249
00:14:50,470 --> 00:14:51,380
Supermarket.

250
00:15:01,540 --> 00:15:02,690
Qing, which one do you want?

251
00:15:02,710 --> 00:15:04,230
I'm not hungry. You eat.

252
00:15:24,210 --> 00:15:25,260
Are you full?

253
00:15:25,450 --> 00:15:26,960
Yes, I'm full.

254
00:15:26,990 --> 00:15:28,040
Let's start.

255
00:15:28,180 --> 00:15:29,480
Start what?

256
00:15:29,700 --> 00:15:31,030
The scene simulation.

257
00:15:44,120 --> 00:15:46,290
Five bottles of water, 20 liters.

258
00:15:46,320 --> 00:15:47,800
Around 20 kilograms.

259
00:15:47,980 --> 00:15:49,470
The two arms and two legs

260
00:15:49,500 --> 00:15:51,450
were 19 kilograms in total.

261
00:15:57,210 --> 00:15:59,120
[Timing]

262
00:16:03,300 --> 00:16:06,620
[Xinfeng Road Qianzhuang Village Intersection]

263
00:16:09,590 --> 00:16:13,970
[Xinfeng Road Qianzhuang Village Intersection]

264
00:16:15,560 --> 00:16:16,600
How long was that?

265
00:16:17,540 --> 00:16:19,110
One hour and five minutes.

266
00:16:19,240 --> 00:16:20,560
An hour?

267
00:16:24,430 --> 00:16:26,000
I thought this 923 meters

268
00:16:26,030 --> 00:16:28,240
would take half an hour to and fro.

269
00:16:28,300 --> 00:16:29,850
I didn't expect that it took more than an hour.

270
00:16:30,420 --> 00:16:30,900
No.

271
00:16:31,940 --> 00:16:33,520
The time cost is too high.

272
00:16:33,940 --> 00:16:35,500
The time cost is very important

273
00:16:35,500 --> 00:16:37,310
to the murderer.

274
00:16:37,330 --> 00:16:38,910
Besides, only the four limbs were buried here.

275
00:16:39,100 --> 00:16:40,430
The other body parts

276
00:16:40,560 --> 00:16:42,500
must be buried in at least two other places.

277
00:16:42,530 --> 00:16:44,090
My deduction was wrong.

278
00:16:52,710 --> 00:16:53,500
Qing.

279
00:16:53,620 --> 00:16:55,420
We found a returning car at the intersection

280
00:16:55,480 --> 00:16:57,110
of Qianzhuang Village and Xinfeng Road.

281
00:16:57,420 --> 00:16:58,670
What kind of car is it?

282
00:16:58,690 --> 00:17:00,140
A silver-gray minivan.

283
00:17:00,160 --> 00:17:02,580
